collectionMetadata.name: Nature Reserves Gazette 2005
collectionMetadata.description: Gazetted land parcels details of the four nature reserves of Singapore under The Parks and Trees Act 2005. These land lot parcels were digitally capturedin 1995, and checked against SLA dataset obtained from the Land System Support Unit then.The lots' details were again updated and verified with SLA Office when the Parks and Trees Act were prepared in early 2000s.
